talent_desc: Symbiote host gains 25% increased Attack Speed.
Symbiote\'s Carapace increases the Movement Speed of the target by 40% for 3.5 seconds.
Locust Basic Attacks cleave for 50% damage, and explode on death for 224 (107 + 4% per level) damage.
Increases Toxic Nest\'s range to global and increases duration by 25%.
Locust\'s Basic Attacks become a long-range siege attack that deal 70% more damage.
Activate to calldown a Mule that repairs Structures, one at a time, near target point for 40 seconds, healing for 100 Health every 1 second. Grants 1 ammo every 3 seconds.
Toxic Nests deal 75% more damage over 3 seconds.
Your Symbiote\'s Spike Burst also slows enemy Movement Speed by 40% for 2 seconds.
Monstrosity gains the ability to Deep Tunnel to any visible location once every 25 seconds.
As long as the Ultimate Evolution is alive, the original target of the clone gains a Shield equal to 25% of their maximum Health. Refreshes every 5 seconds.

Turn an allied Minion or Locust into a Monstrosity. When enemy Minions or captured Mercenaries near the Monstrosity die, it gains 5% Health and 5% Basic Attack damage, stacking up to 40 times. The Monstrosity takes 50% less damage from Minions and Structures.Using Symbiote on the Monstrosity allows you to control it, in addition to Symbiote\'s normal benefits.
Symbiote creates an additional Symbiote on a nearby allied Hero. This Symbiote mimics the commands of the first, but does half the damage and shielding.
Activate to spawn 3 Locusts at a nearby location.
Activate to create a nest that periodically spawns Locusts. Only one Locust Nest can be active at a time.
Increases the damage and range of Symbiote\'s Stab by 20%.
Using Symbiote\'s Carapace also applies an untalented Carapace Shield to all nearby allied Heroes, Minions, and Mercenaries.
Increases the range of Symbiote\'s Spike Burst by 25% and decreases the cooldown by 1 second.
Reduces the cooldown of Toxic Nest by 2 seconds and adds 2 additional charges.
Symbiote\'s Carapace heals the target for 149 (71 + 4% per level) Health per second over 4 seconds.
Symbiote\'s Spike Burst heals the host for 141 (67 + 4% per level) Health per enemy Hero hit.
Symbiote\'s Stab gains 1 additional charge and its cooldown is reduced by 0.5 seconds.
Increases Locust\'s Health by 50% and duration by 40%.
Increases the Shield amount of Symbiote\'s Carapace by 40% and allows it to persist after Symbiote ends.

Clone target allied Hero and control it for 20 seconds. Abathur has perfected the clone, granting it 20% Ability Power, 20% bonus Attack Damage, and 10% bonus Movement Speed. Cannot use their Heroic Ability.
Toxic Nests slow enemy Movement Speed by 40% for 2.5 seconds.
Ultimate Evolution clones and Monstrosities deal 301 (143 + 4% per level) damage to nearby enemies every 3 seconds and when they die.
Increases the max range of Impale by 25%.
Upon taking Ability Damage, reduce that damage and further Ability Damage by 50% for 1.5 seconds. Can only trigger once every 8 seconds.
Increases the attack damage of spawned Beetles by 30%.
Quest: Gathering a Regeneration Globe increases your Health Regeneration by 1 per second, up to 30. Reward: After gathering 30 Regeneration Globes, you also gain 500 Health.
Increases Burrow Charge range by 20% and damage by 100%.
Basic Attacks deal 50% of your Basic Attack Damage in an area around the target.
Anub\'arak automatically spawns Beetles every 8 seconds. Can be toggled on and off.
Using Harden Carapace also increases Anub\'arak\'s Movement Speed by 30% for 3 seconds.
Increases Harden Carapace\'s Shield amount by 40%.
Beetles heal you for 50% of their damage with each attack if you are nearby.
Deal 145 (69 + 4% per level) damage per second in an area around yourself. Each enemy damaged heals you for 40 (19 + 4% per level) Health. Lasts 8 seconds.
Wraps target enemy Hero in a cocoon, rendering them unable to act or be targeted for 8 seconds. Allies of the Hero can attack the cocoon to break it and free them early.
Deal 23 damage per second to nearby enemies.
Casting Harden Carapace will also deal 176 (84 + 4% per level) damage to nearby enemies.
Create a bed of spikes along Impale\'s path that slows enemy Move Speed by 30% and deals 101 (48 + 4% per level) damage per second. Spikes persist for 3.5 seconds.
Increases Burrow Charge impact area by 85% and lowers the cooldown by 4 seconds for each Hero hit.
Every 3rd Basic Attack against enemy Heroes sapwns a Beetle.
Activate to deal 10% of target enemy Hero\'s Max Health and heal for twice that amount.

Anub\'arak gains a permanent Vampire Locust that attacks a nearby enemy every 3 seconds. The Vampire Locust deals 336 (160 + 4% per level) damage and returns to heal Anub\'arak for 82 (39 + 4% per level) health.
Staying near the Coccon allows Anub\'arak to extend the duration by up to 4 seconds per Cocoon.
Activate to reduce damage taken by 75% for 4 seconds.
Activate to reset the cooldowns of your Basic Abilities.
Activating Twin Blades reduces the damage received from the next Hero Basic Attack by 75%. Can store up to 2 charges.
Twin Blades attacks deal 150% bonus damage versus non-Heroic enemies.

Quest: Every Minion killed near you grants 0.2 Attack Damage, and Takedowns grant 0.5 Attack Damage.Reward: Upon gaining 40 bonus Attack Damage, you can also activate Seasoned Marksman to increase your Attack Speed by 40% for 3 seconds. 60 second cooldown.
Cooldown Reduction gained by hitting Heroes with Blade Dash is increased to 4 seconds.
Shield Overload\'s cooldown recharges 50% faster while the shield is active, and increases the duration of Shielf Overload from 5 to 6 seconds.
Shield Overload\'s shield amount is increased by 80% while you are below 25% Max Health.
Increases the damage of the first dash of Blade Dash by 150%.
Phase Prism also slows the enemy\'s Movement Speed by 35% for 4 seconds.
Hitting an enemy Hero with Phase Prism grants 50% bonus Attack Speed for 4 seconds.
After using an ability, your next Basic Attack within 6 seconds deals 40% additional damage.
Fire a large area pulse from the Spear of Adun, dealing 250 damage and Blinding enemies for 4 seconds. Unlimited range.
Target an enemy Hero with an orbital beam from the Spear of Adun, dealing 404 damage per second for 8 seconds. The beam will chase the target as they move. Unlimited range.
Blade Dash cooldown recharges 100% faster while you are below 50% Health.
Increases Twin Blades\'s number of Basic Attacks to 3 but increase its cooldown by 1 second..
Phase Prism pulls and damages an additional enemy Hero near the first.
When Shield Overload activates, you take 40% less damage from Abilities for 4 seconds.
Increase Twin Blades\' charge distance by 100%.
Twin Blades attacks against Heroes deal an additional 2.5% of the target\'s maximum Health in damage.
Twin Blades final strike causes enemy Heroes to become Vulnerable for 2 seconds, increasing all damage taken by 25%.
While Shield Overload is active, you deal 50 damage a second to nearby enemies.
Suppression Pulse gains an additional charge. There is a 10 second cooldown between uses.
If the target of Purifier Beam dies, it automatically recasts on the nearest enemy Hero.
Increases Shield Overload\'s cooldown reduction from Basic Attacks to 6 seconds.
Basic Attacks deal 20% more damage and slow enemy Movement Speed by 20% for 1 second.
Every 5 seconds, you can Block a Basic Attack from an enemy Hero reducing its damage by 50%. Stores up to 2 charges.

Quest: Using Frostmourne Hungers on an enemy Hero permanently increases the Mana it restores by 4, up to 40. Reward: After hitting 10 Heroes with Frostmourne Hungers, also increase its damage bonus by 25%.
Howling Blast\'s cooldown is reduced by 5 seconds when it hits an enemy Hero.
Frozen Tempest Mana cost reduced by 4 per second.
Reduce Death Coil\'s cooldown by 2 seconds and increase its range by 25%.
Frozen Tempest damage increased by 50%.
Every 3rd Basic Attack heals you for 4% of your max Health.
You gain the healing effect of Death Coil even when you use it on enemies. If you damage an enemy Hero with it, you also heal for an additional 100% of the damage dealt.
Activate to reduce damage taken by 25% and reduce the duration of silences, stuns, slows, roots, and polymorphs agaisnt you by 75% for 3 seconds.
Summons Ghouls that last 15 seconds. Sacrifice Ghouls to heal for 586 Health.
Deals 504 damage and slows enemies by 60% for 2 seconds. Also disables non-Heroic enemies and Structures for 20 seconds.
Increases Howling Blast\'s range by 30% and causes it to also root enemies between you and the target for 1.25 seconds.
Reduces Frostmourne Hungers\' cooldown by 2 seconds. Frostmourne Hungers also slows the enemy by 40% for 1.5 seconds.

Enemy Heroes that remain within Frozen Tempest for 3 seconds are rooted for 1.75 seconds. This effect only happen once every 10 seconds.
Increased application to your next 2 Basic Attacks.
Death Coil deals 10% more damage for each 10% of life you are missing.
3 additional Ghouls are created. Ghouls heal for an additional 50% and last 5 seconds longer.
Sindragosa flies twice as far. Enemy Heroes are rooted for 2 seconds, and then slowed by 60% for 3.5 seconds.
Passively increases your Movement Speed by 10%. Activate to increase this bonus to 30% for 3 seconds.

reate an expanding nova of wind, dealing 699 (332 + 4% per level) damage and pushing enemies away. Also passively increases the healing of Soothing Mist by 8%.

After a 3 second delay, fire explodes around you dealing 1096 (520 + 4% per level) damage to enemies.Can be cast while using Ruthless Onslaught.

Throw a hitching post that attaches to the nearest enemy Hero after a 1 second delay. This deals 375 (178 + 4% per level) damage and causes the enemy to be chained to the post and Silenced for 3 seconds.
Basic Attack deal 35% of your Basic Attack Damage in an area around the target.

Roll around inside an Unstoppable barrel, dealing 130 (62 + 4% per level) damage to enemies in the way and knocking them back. Lasts for 5 seconds.
